---
title: Sticky Double Halloumi & Spiced Potatoes with Garden Salad & Crushed Peanuts
description: Apricot sauce is a crowd favourite and we want to put it on everything! Halloumi is up next and once again, this sauce has outdone itself. The salty halloumi gets a little sweeter and with a side of golden, Mumbai-spiced potatoes, what more could you ask for?
